<p>298. JUA 27/02/2013. Case no. OMN 1/2013. State Replies: 20/03/2013; 21/03/2013. 
Alleged hunger strike started by eleven human rights defenders detained at Samail Central 
Prison, to protest their sentencing as well as delays in processing their cases at the Muscat 
Court of Appeals. 
