as well as offline, including in the context of elections, and <i>including persons espousing 
minority or dissenting views or beliefs</i>, human rights defenders, trade unionists and others, 
including migrants, seeking to exercise or to promote these rights&#8221; (emphasis added). 
</p>
<p><b>  Russian Federation 
</b></p>
