<p><b>  Zimbabwe 
</b></p>
<p>453. JAL 22/03/2012. Case no. ZWE 4/2012. State Reply: None to date. Follow up on an 
alleged illegal decision suspending the activities of 29 NGOs in Masvingo. 
</p>
<p>454. JAL 29/03/2012. Case no. ZWE 5/2012. State Reply: None to date. Alleged 
