<p>455. JUA 17/08/2012. Case no ZWE 6/2012. State Reply: None to date. Alleged arrest, 
detention and ill treatment of 44 members of Gays and Lesbians of Zimbabwe (GALZ).  
</p>
<p>456. JAL 17/10/2012. Case no. ZWE 8/2012. State Reply: None to date. Alleged repeated 
acts of harassment against leaders of two human rights associations reportedly operating as 
unregistered organisations.  
